LOAD calc_credit_debt 150
RELOAD calc_credit_debt
CATCH api_failure flag_api_call_error 1
MAP calc_credit_debt
MOUT pay_debt 1
MOUT deposit 2
MOUT get_mpesa 3
MOUT send_mpesa 4
MOUT back 0
MOUT quit 9
HALT
INCMP ^ 0
INCMP pay_debt 1
INCMP pool_deposit 2
INCMP get_mpesa 3
INCMP send_mpesa 4
INCMP quit 9
INCMP . *
